{"tid":1507376,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"向警隊處理七警案學習","createTime":"2019-08-26T06:26:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T06:41:21.000Z","uid":302559,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"48da4571864e55d0cba305d19eaec5f6779b6588","tid":1507376,"uid":302559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T06:26:34.000Z","msg":"有一個諗法：<br />\n如果非染紅機構因商業考慮被迫跪低，其實可以向警隊對七警嘅處理方法學習，仲要有咁高調得咁高調。<br />\n舉個例，要因為言論問題炒工會主席嚟交差，可以喺炒嘅時候提供一筆極豐厚嘅補償金，明眼人一睇就知係安家費。補償金唔夠豐厚唔緊要，可以公開接受其他私人捐助。想做得盡啲，仲可以用被炒同事嘅名義成立一啲具紀念性質嘅項目，例如成立獎學金滲透中小學。<br />\n總之，要令對家知道，你向我施壓要我炒自己人，唔緊要，我要佢犧牲得風風光光。結果係就算有人想督灰都唔會做，免得益咗烈士。"},{"pid":"9cdcc86425daf7bfb571eb340aa4ef1211ac183d","tid":1507376,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T06:26:47.000Z","msg":"唔好意思借個post宣傳一下<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4GJMrJb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4GJMrJb.jpg&h=cb7c9807&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n901 和你塞  13:00 見   <a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTY7ScfX6drAaaDYLMstvIIS4%3D&h=a539efb4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a>"},{"pid":"17a776a1e0f63b4e7d3b0d4f0b13ffe4776fc2ad","tid":1507376,"uid":56052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T06:41:21.000Z","msg":"(外國文宣) 大家係咪miss 左一粒核彈？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1507386\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1507386</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}